Here\'s the challenge:

Using whatever mods you like, (MechJeb is recomended) create a giant space station. but here\'s the kicker;

**Send it up in multiple pieces and 'dock' it together.**

let the awesomeness begin ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif)

Sorry, forgot to mention;

NO auto orbit hacks.

please make a video or take screen shots of your journey!
